title: Elasticsearch pending tasks
agents: linux
catalog: app/Elasticsearch
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check uses the special agent for elasticsearch. The pending task count and
 growth per minute will be recorded and averaged for a set amount of time
 (30 minutes by default). The last recent pending task count growth
 will be compared to this average value. Thresholds can be set on how much higher
 the last recent growth can be compared to the average growth.

item:
 No item

inventory:
 One service for the cluster

perfdata:
 Total pending tasks, growth within the last minute and average
 growth per minute
